Installation
============

The PAN syntax file for VIM can be installed with the following process:
mkdir -p ${HOME}/.vim/ftdetect
mkdir ${HOME}/.vim/syntax

Create the file ${HOME}/.vim/ftdetect/pan.vim with the following content:
au BufRead,BufNewFile *.tpl set filetype=pan
au BufRead,BufNewFile *.pan set filetype=pan

Download the file pan.vim from the quattor website:
https://quattor.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/quattor/trunk/pan/panc-vim/pan.vim

and copy it to the ${HOME}/.vim/syntax directory.

